*gentoo-sources-2.6.23-r3 (27 Nov 2007)

  27 Nov 2007; Daniel Drake <dsd@gentoo.org>
  +gentoo-sources-2.6.23-r3.ebuild:
  Update to Linux 2.6.23.9. Fix missing USB attributes in sysfs. Fix 7 hour
  boot delay for buggy forcedeth hardware.

*gentoo-sources-2.6.23-r2 (17 Nov 2007)

  17 Nov 2007; Daniel Drake <dsd@gentoo.org>
  +gentoo-sources-2.6.23-r2.ebuild:
  Update to Linux 2.6.23.8. Fix ACPI thermal check stack overflow.

