  gentoo-sources-2.6.23.ebuild:
  Add ~ia64/~sparc

  25 Oct 2007; Jose Luis Rivero <yoswink@gentoo.org>
  gentoo-sources-2.6.22-r8.ebuild:
  Stable on alpha. This solves some issues related to fdatasync defined but
  unimplemented which was breaking mysql with the error 'Can't sync file
  mysqld-bin.index' errno(78)

  18 Oct 2007; Luca Barbato <lu_zero@gentoo.org>
  gentoo-sources-2.6.23.ebuild:
  Marked ~ppc ~ppc64

