  zd1211 USB-WLAN devices. Fix resume of hda-intel sigmatel codecs. Fix
  detection of Logitech QuickCam microphone. Fix AHCI/ATI boot problems. Fix
  mouse probing on HP-500. Re-enable 88E8056 ethernet support in sky2. Fix
  crash with sis900 ethernet hardware.

